                                            "Day_14"))

                                                              as.vector(sample_data(physeq)$treatment))),
                                                levels = c("H2O",
                                                           "Eubiotic",
                                                           "Normobiotic",
                                                           "Dysbiotic",
                                                           "DSS",
                                                           "Predni"))
